<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>InnoDB</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>全文索引采用反向索引（倒排索引）设计。反向索引存储单词列表，对于每个单词，存储单词出现在其中的文档列表。为了支持邻近搜索，还存储每个单词的位置信息，作为字节偏移</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=379 height=463 alt=正排与倒排索引的区别></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>反向索引（倒排索引）将每一个单词作为索引项，根据该索引项查找包含该单词的文档。因此，索引都是单词和唯一记录文档的标识是一对多的关系。将索引单词排序，根据排序后的单词定位找到包含该单词的文档。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>

     margin-bottom:7pt'><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt'>反向索引（倒排索引）存储了单词与单词自身在一个或多个文档中所在的位置之间的映射。这通常利用关联数组实现，其拥有两种表现形式。</span></li>
 <ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
  0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;

      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";

      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";

     font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333' lang=zh-CN>只能根据单词找到对应的文档，而</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333'
     lang=zh-CN>full inverted index</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333' lang=zh-CN>不仅能找到对应的文档，还能找到单词在文档中的具体位置。</span><span

     12.0pt;color:black' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333' lang=zh-CN>inverted file index</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>，</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
     12.0pt;color:black' lang=zh-CN>full inverted index </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>占用了更多的空间，但是能更好的定位数据，并扩充一些其他搜索特性。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:13.5pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>反向索引（倒排索引）的原理</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle;color:#333333'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333'
     lang=zh-CN>全文索引的建立过程有两个阶段，先将分词存入</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:#333333' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:black' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index Cache</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>（全文检索索引缓存），然后再批量更新到</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt;color:black' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:black' lang=zh-CN>Auxiliary Table</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;color:black'
     lang=zh-CN>（辅助表）中</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=257 height=348></p>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>FTS Index Cache</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>（全文检索索引缓存）</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>在事务提交的时候将分词写入到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
     Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>InnoDB</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>会批量对</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
     Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>进行更新，为了提高性能不会插入一条数据立刻更新到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Auxiliary
     Table</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>。进行批量更新的几种情况： </span></li>
 <ol type=1 style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:
  0in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
  font-style:normal'>
  <li value=1 style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:
      normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=zh-CN>全文检索索引缓存已满，默认大小为</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>32M</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，可以通过修改</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>innodb_ft_cache_size</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
      font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>来改变</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index Cache</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;
      font-style:normal;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的大小</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>关闭数据库的时候，将</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
      Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中的数据库会同步到磁盘上的</span><span style='font-family:
      "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Auxiliary Table</span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当对全文检索进行查询时，首先会将在</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
      Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中对应的字段合并到</span><span style='font-family:
      "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Auxiliary
      Table</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=zh-CN>中，然后在进行查询</span></li>
  <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当数据库突然宕机时，可能会导致一些</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
      Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中的数据未同步到</span><span style='font-family:
      "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>Auxiliary
      Table</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
      lang=zh-CN>上。</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
      font-size:11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>数据库重启时，当用户对表进行全文检索时，</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>InnoDB</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>存储引擎会自动读取未完成的文档，然后进行分词操作，在将分词的结果放入到</span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>FTS Index
      Cache</span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.0pt'
      lang=zh-CN>中。</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
      11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>innodb_ft_cache_size</span><span style='font-family:
      "Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
      style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的大小会影响恢复的时间</span></li>
 </ol>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:1.5in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'><span
     style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>Index Cache</span><span style='font-family:
     "Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>是一个红黑树结构，其根据（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>word</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>ilist</span><span

</ul>

font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS"'>Auxiliary Table</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>（辅助表）</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>正如前面所说的，倒排索引需要将</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>word</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存放到一张表中，这个表称为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Auxiliary Table</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>（辅助表）</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>InnoDB</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>存储引擎中，为了提高全文检索的并行性能，共有</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>6</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>张</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Auxiliary Table</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，目前每张表根据</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>word</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>的</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>Latin</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>编码进行分区</span></li>
</ul>
